WEBVTT

00:00:29.057 --> 00:00:31.173
Prije nekoliko godina

00:00:31.197 --> 00:00:33.694
rekli su mi da patim od tjeskobe

00:00:33.718 --> 00:00:34.868
i depresije,

00:00:35.289 --> 00:00:37.709
dva stanja koja često idu zajedno.

00:00:38.073 --> 00:00:42.338
Prije to nikome ne bih rekla,

00:00:42.362 --> 00:00:44.822
pogotovo ne pred grupom ljudi.

00:00:44.846 --> 00:00:46.373
Kao Afroamerikanka,

00:00:46.397 --> 00:00:50.037
morala sam se jako potruditi
da nešto postignem.

00:00:50.061 --> 00:00:52.040
Kao i mnogi drugi u mojoj zajednici,

00:00:52.064 --> 00:00:55.872
mislila sam da je depresija slabost,

00:00:55.896 --> 00:00:57.432
karakterna mana.

00:00:57.456 --> 00:00:59.030
Ali nisam bila slaba,

00:00:59.054 --> 00:01:00.524
bila sam veoma uspješna.